name: cat-pic-finder
description:
"# cat-finder" A cat finder app for searching cat pictures which you can sort your image type by check/unchecking the options between png, gif, jpeg images.
Search field can be used to find particular catagory like cats with boxes, cloth, hats, space, sunglasses ties.
Any catagory not available will display error message and if search field left blank will display random cat pictures.
